messages.content: What is our annual revenue for 2024?
Our annual revenue for 2024 is $8.5 Million, representing a 63% year-over-year growth from the $5.2 Million in revenue generated in 2023.
who is the ceo and whats the background?
Sarah Johnson is the CEO of the company. She has a background as the former VP of Engineering at Google Cloud (8 years) and holds an MBA from Stanford GSB and a BS Computer Science from MIT.
how many total customers do we have?

We currently have a total of 550 active customers, representing an increase from the initial 450 companies that were part of our Active Customers list. This represents a growth rate of 22% over the past month.
Our lead investor is Andreessen Horowitz (a16z), with Sequoia Capital also participating in the funding rounds.
